The evidence with the title 'Rick Perry proposes letting states opt out of social security ... ' says Nov 6, 2010  ... “ in 1981, Matagorda, Brazoria, and Galveston Counties all opted out of the Social Security program for their employees . Today, their program is very, very well- funded and there is no question about whether it's going to be funded  ... I think , let the states decide if that 's what's best for their cities, ” Perry replied. 
